name: Hi, Hello - 8 x 10 Print
description:
"Hi, Hello" - 8" x 10" (20 x 25 cm) giclee print.

...pleased to meet you.

• Print (paper) size is 8.5" x 11", image size is 8" x 10". Please note the small white border for framing.
